translation: The warriors are striking the daggers, holding them tightly and coming face to face and the brave fighters are challenging one another, roaring like the lions.

translation: The firm limbs, after swinging continuously, are falling down and the brave and beautiful fighters, fearlessly coming face to face with others are clashing.20.

transliteration: Navan Nisaan Baajeeyan|| Ghataa Ghamannd Laajeeyan||
translation: Listening to the resonance of the trumpets, the clouds are feeling shy.

transliteration: Taball Toundran Baje|| Sounant Soormaa Gade||21||
translation: The fastened trumpets have resounded and haring their sound, the warriors are thundering.21.

transliteration: Su Joojh(i) Kai Darain|| Sures Log Bichrain||
